{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":18687,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3202,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"有！超喜欢花满楼","timestamp":1592843060,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18711,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3202,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"如果不是一部里面同时喜欢几个人的话应该不算渣吧","timestamp":1592843169,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18729,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3202,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"有的有的（作为对比金庸的基本没看过","timestamp":1592843278,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18733,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3202,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"读过部分古龙的作品，总觉得古龙笔下的江湖太狭小，只能容得下主角与反派，与想象中的江湖气不太相符。（求轻喷）","timestamp":1592843290,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18736,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3202,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"而且感觉古龙的套路就是好看的妹子脱光了诱惑男主，楚留香如是，陆小凤如是。本来看完凤舞九天觉得陆小凤和沙曼修成正果了，结果剑神一笑里面牛肉汤又出来了","timestamp":1592843312,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18742,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3202,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 每个人心目中的江湖都不一样吧","timestamp":1592843338,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18755,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3202,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 古龙的江湖在心里在天上，金庸的江湖在门外在人间","timestamp":1592843401,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18757,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3202,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 是的，不过古龙开车的确比金庸厉害不少","timestamp":1592843405,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18786,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3202,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 对比金庸，的确金庸的江湖系统比较完整，古龙常常想到哪儿写哪儿，还经常自己埋下的伏笔写丢了。但古龙会有很多细节触动我，一语点醒梦中人的感觉。至于江湖非正即邪，我觉得古龙笔下的坏人常常有苦衷，也算不那么黑白分明吧。但像楚留香陆小凤那样几乎完美的主角我不大喜欢，更喜欢李寻欢这种有缺憾的或者小鱼儿这种逐渐成长的","timestamp":1592843580,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18802,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3202,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 感觉你这么一说的确很有道理，古龙的侠更注重潇洒，也更为理想化，侧重于仗剑走天涯，而金庸的侠更讲究入世，侧重于行侠仗义。","timestamp":1592843713,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18833,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3202,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 嗯。求仁得仁","timestamp":1592843857,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18847,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3202,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"单从武学角度看，古龙笔下一些武功没有层次感，常常一出手就是秒杀，高手对决就是两个无穷大比较，最后阿列夫零败给了阿列夫一。金庸笔下的武力值则可以用100以内的自然数表示。两种各有妙处吧，古龙笔下燕十三和谢晓峰一战以及小李飞刀例不虚发算是能最触动我的，金庸的名场面如聚贤庄 三战  围攻东方似乎更多一些。","timestamp":1592843930,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":3,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":3202,"reply":12,"tag":null,"text":"有没有古龙粉啊。最近看了陆小凤传奇，感觉古龙每部小说换个女主显得陆小凤好渣啊","timestamp":1592843031,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782584,"url":"","vote":{}}}